channel.title: Problem solved
channel.description:
[code] Error: T2 - 246,71,164 - 6,0,0 - 120,9,0,-56,59,-26, [/code]
Anyone know how to fix this? It works fine for anyone else that uses the Client, just gives me that error when I try to log into my server, yes other people have used it on my server.
Edit: ++ For helping me fix this..
Problem solved..

item.title: Problem solved
item.dc:creator: @kniveslives kniveslives
item.description:
@kniveslives wrote:

Well I found out it was because the Client I was using didn’t have the new Silab ID’s on it, and my character was wearing skillcapes and such, so I couldn’t log in with it.
